This is the <B>CAMPAIGN</B> page <br><br>
<h1 align = "center"> Select Front, Campaign and Sub-Campaign - then a top level unit in that sub campaign</h1>
<h2> Programming Notes</h2>
<p>First select a Front</p>
<p>Second select a Campaign from that Front</p>
<p>Third select a SubCampaign from that Campaign</p>
<p>Finally select a top level Unit from that Sub Campaign</p>
<p> Store the selections in the Sesionvars table</p>
<p>At any point you can change the selection - but doing so loses all selections below the one changed</p>
<p>e.g. if you change Front you lose Campaign, Subcampaign and Unit.  If you change Campaign you lose SubCampaign and Unit.  If you change Subcampaign you lose only the Unit</p>
<p>It is not permitted to leave the page until ALL four items are selected - may be a problem to achieve</p>

